Comment: Standard opening, i was expecting something different but hey just playin chess.

Just what I had expected, the old queen bishop mate.  Kind of an insult but i'm still cautious.

hoping to take a free knight.

No give, so this is my favorite part of the game.  I knew that if I could get his feisty knight out of the way then I have mate shortly.  So i thought that i'd offer my knight for free because i'm only a "1220" player
I had to wait two days to see if he takes or not......
Oh baby!!  I was going nuts at this point.  Do you see it???

POW!  he resigned at this point.  I hate it when i get a resignation when mate is only a move away.  what a bitch but, whatever.  e2 or e1 only legal move fatal when my black beauty takes his Knight.    Upon resignation Decebals said that i played strong for my rating, I think that he didnt play strong enough for his.  Only in this game, he killed me on the next one.  Either way, I think that the moral of the story is, if your opponent underestimates you, make sure that he regrets it.  I received 19.4 points with this win.
